<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Letter OF Authorization</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .header,
    .footer {
      position: fixed;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px 0;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .header {
      top: 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #b4b4b4;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .header small {
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin: 0 0 5px;
      display: block;
    }

    .header h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .footer {
      bottom: 0;
      border-top: 1px solid #b4b4b4;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .footer p {
      margin: 0;
    }

    .content {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 100px auto 50px auto;
      padding: 10px 0;
    }

    .letterhead {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .letterhead p {
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .letterhead p strong {
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .signature {
      margin-top: 50px;
    }

    .d-flex {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .sn_img {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .sn_img img {
      margin: 0 auto 4px;
      display: block;
    }

    .sn_img small {
      font-size: 10px;
    }

    @media print {
      .content {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 10px auto;
        padding: 10px 0;
      }
      .page-break {
        page-break-before: always;
        margin-bottom: 0px;
      }
      .header,
      .footer {
        position: relative;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Fixed Header -->
  <div class="header">
    <h2><%= entityName %></h2>
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="https://dev.cryptoindia.in/logo.svg" width="110" class="img-fluid" alt="Logo" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Letter Content -->
  <div class="content">
    <div class="letterhead">
      <p><strong> BOARD RESOLUTION </strong><br>
        FOR APPOINTMENT OF AUTHORIZED SIGNATORY
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="date">
      <p>Date: <%= resolutionDate %></p>
    </div>

    <p>CERTIFIED TRUE COPY OF THE RESOLUTION PASSED IN THE MEETING OF THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS/ PARTNERS OF 
      <b><%= companyName %></b> HELD ON <b><%= resolutionDate %></b> AT <b><%= resolutionTime %></b>, 
      AT <b><%= companyAddress %></b>.
    </p>

    <p>Resolved that:</p>

    <p>
      The Board of Directors/Partners approves the opening of an account and authorizes the company to avail all
      necessary services offered by <b>CRYPTO INDIA (INCRYP BLOCKCHAIN PRIVATE LIMITED)</b>.
    </p>

    <p>The following person are hereby authorized to:</p>

    <table border="1" style="text-align:center; border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;">
      <thead style="font-size:12px; text-align:center;">
        <tr>
          <th style="padding:10px;">NAME OF AUTHORIZED PERSON</th>
          <th style="padding:10px;">PAN NUMBER</th>
          <th style="padding:10px;">PHONE NUMBER & EMAIL ID</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% authorizedPersons.forEach(person => { %>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:10px;"><%= person.name %></td>
            <td style="padding:10px;"><%= person.pan %></td>
            <td style="padding:10px;">
              <%= person.phone %><br><%= person.email %>
            </td>
          </tr>
        <% }) %>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p><small>The meeting was called to discuss and pass the board resolution with the participation of the following
        directors.</small></p>

    <table border="1" style="text-align:center; border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;">
      <thead style="font-size:12px; text-align:center;">
        <tr>
          <th style="padding:10px;">NAME</th>
          <th style="padding:10px;">PAN NUMBER</th>
          <th style="padding:10px;">EMAIL ID</th>
          <th style="padding:10px;">Signature</th>
          <th style="padding:10px;">Photo</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% directors.forEach(director => { %>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:10px;"><%= director.name %></td>
            <td style="padding:10px;"><%= director.panNumber %></td>
            <td style="padding:10px;"><%= director.email %></td>
            <td style="padding:10px;">
              <div class="sn_img">
                <% if (director.signature) { %>
                  <img src="<%= director.signature %>" width="100" />
                  <small><%= director.signedAt %></small>
                <% } else { %>
                  <span style="color:gray;">No Signature</span>
                <% } %>
              </div>
            </td>
            <td style="padding:10px;">
              <div class="sn_img">
                <% if (director.photo) { %>
                  <img src="<%= director.photo %>" width="80" />
                  <small><%= director.photoAt %></small>
                <% } else { %>
                  <span style="color:gray;">No Photo</span>
                <% } %>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        <% }) %>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- Fixed Footer -->
  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2025 Crypto India | www.cryptoindia.in | support@cryptoindia.in </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
